{"tid":796654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[左癌誤國]德國一男子俾兩難民殺咗 暴發反移民示威 與左翼\"支持者起衝突 政府譴責\"在街上散播仇恨\"","createTime":"2018-08-28T02:21:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-29T05:07:36.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"c51877f2a82bb1097a9c4307bae79875244a1bd2","tid":796654,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T02:21:10.000Z","msg":"德國兇殺案導致移民遭追打　左右翼示威爆衝突<br />\n1569出版時間：2018/08/28 07:49  \t<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180828/640_e6dd5afd35fa344630baf4334e33235c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180828%2F640_e6dd5afd35fa344630baf4334e33235c.jpg&h=a007654f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n歐新－埃菲社<br />\n德國東部城巿肯尼茲（Chemnitz）周日凌晨有一名德國男子因涉及口角衝突而喪生，一名敘利亞青年及一名伊拉克青年遭控涉案。這起涉及移民的兇殺案，在周日與周一接連引發示威，周一的示威中，極右翼示威者與反右翼示威者爆發激烈衝突，造成至少6人受傷。<br />\n <br />\n德新社報導，周日凌晨的兇殺案中，喪生者是一名35歲德國男子，另有2名男子受重傷。一名23敘利亞人及一名22歲伊拉克人已被捕，檢方指控他們「沒有正當理由」攻擊受害者。<br />\n <br />\n當天有800名示威者上街抗議這起兇殺案，向警察丟擲水瓶和石塊。網友在網路發布的影片顯示，示威中有移民遭攻擊，震驚德國社會。政府發言人賽柏特（Steffen Seibert）隨即譴責針對移民的暴力：「我們不會接受這種暴民行徑：追打外表、血緣和我們不同的人，或試圖在街頭散播仇恨。」<br />\n <br />\n到了周一，則有2000名極右翼示威者走上街頭，與大約1000名反右翼示威者爆發激烈衝突。警方奮力將雙方隔開，在雙方陣營中間噴水砲。左翼人士高喊「納粹無權宣傳」、「將民族社會主義逐出人心」。<br />\n <br />\n左翼黨（Die Linke party）黨魁德茲納（Tim Detzner）說：「追獵外表看似外國人的行動，是一大警訊。我們要展現齊尼茲也有另一面：向世界開放，反對仇外情緒。」右翼示威者則高舉德國民族主義標語。<br />\n <br />\n警方表示，雙方互擲爆竹與其他物品，起初有2人受傷，另有4名極右翼示威者在離開示威人群時遭攻擊受傷。警方坦承，示威人數出乎預料，派出的警力不足以應付。齊尼茲周一晚間的氣氛仍然緊張，徹夜有警察駐守街頭。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180828/1419157/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180828%2F1419157%2F&d=Mtxf%2FLmfa2MhPr1aEs7il%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=bb1e8c6a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180828%2F1419157%2F&h=b53891bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180828/1419157/</a>"},{"pid":"8f5d3a96b608f7b989e91ee6ad46b0a891166848","tid":796654,"uid":160662,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T02:22:33.000Z","msg":"政府發言人賽柏特（Steffen Seibert）隨即譴責針對移民的暴力：「我們不會接受這種暴民行徑：追打外表、血緣和我們不同的人，或試圖在街頭散播仇恨。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n垃圾, 幾時有大選趕走阿嬸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c03e64c0973291f3599469fe334915357c1e2c1","tid":796654,"uid":55924,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T02:24:08.000Z","msg":"除非每一個難民都殺人<br />\n只係得99%班左膠都會繼續支持"},{"pid":"a0220b9afa213ff94db1b52b89bee0a8c8e43409","tid":796654,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T02:25:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://video.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2018/08/27/1453113443420059876/960x540_MP4_1453113443420059876.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo.dailymail.co.uk%2Fvideo%2Fmol%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2F1453113443420059876%2F960x540_MP4_1453113443420059876.mp4&d=Mtxf%2FLmfa2MhPr1aEs7il%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=f9f1d4bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://video.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2018/08/27/1453113443420059876/960x540_MP4_1453113443420059876.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/08/27/19/4F71143000000578-6102545-image-a-77_1535394971213.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2F19%2F4F71143000000578-6102545-image-a-77_1535394971213.jpg&h=ef30de2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/08/27/20/4F7162FE00000578-6102545-image-a-93_1535397250426.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2F20%2F4F7162FE00000578-6102545-image-a-93_1535397250426.jpg&h=d8e1a8aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/08/27/20/4F716A9600000578-6102545-image-a-96_1535397565112.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2F20%2F4F716A9600000578-6102545-image-a-96_1535397565112.jpg&h=729a23a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/newpix/2018/08/27/20/4F718BA100000578-6102545-Protesters_flank_a_statue_of_Karl_Marx_as_riot_police_gear_up_an-m-136_1535399299947.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fnewpix%2F2018%2F08%2F27%2F20%2F4F718BA100000578-6102545-Protesters_flank_a_statue_of_Karl_Marx_as_riot_police_gear_up_an-m-136_1535399299947.jpg&h=3cba5270&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nThousands of far-right protesters clash with riot police in German city where man was stabbed to death 'by migrants' as vigilante race-hate mobs 'hunt down foreigners'<br />\nA German man, 35, died in early hours of Sunday after being stabbed at a festival in the city of Chemnitz<br />\n<br />\nAn Iraqi man, aged 22, and a Syrian man, aged 23, were arrested on suspicion of murder following the attack<br />\nAround 800 far-right protesters went to the streets following the protest, which saw attacks on minorites<br />\nMerkel's spokesman said he condemns groups 'in the strongest possible terms' after footage emerged of skinheads chasing a man of Arab appearance down the streets and throwing bottles at police<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">A 22-year-old Iraqi and a 23-year-old Syrian have been arrested and charged with murder.</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nThe stabbing happened around 3.15am on the sidelines of a street festival.<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Police have denied rumours that the fight broke out after the alleged sexual harassment of a woman.</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nProsecutor Christine Muecke told reporters Monday the slaying stemmed from a verbal confrontation that escalated. Two men were taken into custody - a 22-year-old Syrian citizen and a 21 year-old Iraqi citizen- and both were held on suspicion of manslaughter, Muecke said. <br />\n<br />\n仲有好多相:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-6102545/German-govt-condemns-far-right-demo-eastern-city-fatal-dispute.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-6102545%2FGerman-govt-condemns-far-right-demo-eastern-city-fatal-dispute.html&d=Mtxf%2FLmfa2MhPr1aEs7il%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=ac333b51\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-6102545/German-govt-condemns-far-right-demo-eastern-city-fatal-dispute.html</a>"},{"pid":"eeab16b6608ce4147171894e2488751e00a4e5f9","tid":796654,"uid":128568,"like":25,"dislike":3,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T02:26:40.000Z","msg":"「將民族社會主義逐出人心」<br />\n<br />\n德國真係比希特拉玩殘,一野搞到德國人世世代代都唔可以有民族自豪感,一有就等於NAZI<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2cd04a467ff8f7548fcddbd6dcd4df37381124a","tid":796654,"uid":48083,"like":31,"dislike":2,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T02:28:27.000Z","msg":"我都覺得暴力唔啱<br />\n之但係<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">暴力衝突就屌到咁大聲<br />\n殺撚咗人嗰啲有冇屌呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"7602e7ce651971647a4297a9b1966a0bf968f48b","tid":796654,"uid":48161,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T02:29:16.000Z","msg":"Heil Deutschland<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3cd6f11a61a7f6f619a2a69c5fb6754f450f0a8","tid":796654,"uid":199145,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T02:30:01.000Z","msg":"老謀比人拉都唔係拉老謀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n德新社報導，周日凌晨的兇殺案中，喪生者是一名35歲德國男子，另有2名男子受重傷。一名23敘利亞人及一名22歲伊拉克人已被捕，檢方指控他們<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「沒有正當理由」攻擊受害者。<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"163f66dc493e0941a231c3cd566fe5973916223d","tid":796654,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T02:30:52.000Z","msg":".......an MP from the far-right political party AfD, Markus Frohnmaier, tweeted: <br />\n<br />\n&quot;If the state is no longer to protect citizens then people take to the streets and protect themselves. It's as simple as that!&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Today it's a citizen's duty to stop the lethal 'knife migration'!&quot; he wrote, alluding to the influx of migrants in recent years. &quot;It could have targeted your father, son or brother!&quot;<br />\n<br />\nSkip Twitter post by @Frohnmaier_AfD<br />\n<br />\nMarkus Frohnmaier<br />\n@Frohnmaier_AfD<br />\n Wenn der Staat die B&uuml;rger nicht mehr sch&uuml;tzen kann, gehen die Menschen auf die Stra&szlig;e und sch&uuml;tzen sich selber. Ganz einfach! Heute ist es B&uuml;rgerpflicht, die todbringendendie &quot;Messermigration&quot; zu stoppen! <br />\nEs h&auml;tte deinen Vater, Sohn oder Bruder treffen k&ouml;nnen!<br />\n<br />\n3:59 AM - Aug 27, 2018<br />\n2,021<br />\n1,517 people are talking about this<br />\nTwitter Ads info and privacy<br />\nReport<br />\nEnd of Twitter post by @Frohnmaier_AfD<br />\n<br />\nAs the heap of wreaths and candles at the spot where the murder occurred grew larger on Monday evening, right-wing demonstrators massed at the Marx monument, and counter-demonstrators gathered close by.<br />\n<br />\nPolice reported Hitler salutes being thrown among the right-wing crowd, where anti-immigration placards can be seen with messages like &quot;Stop the asylum flood&quot;.<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-45324804\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-45324804&d=Mtxf%2FLmfa2MhPr1aEs7il%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=f9863669\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih